  ('optometrist-moex-02914', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '蔡先生兩眼近視可以分別被-10.00 D的眼鏡矯正，有15 mm的頂點距離。當他在看眼鏡前20 cm的手機 時，她的調節需求（accommodative demand）為何？', '["+3.54 D", "+8.70 D", "+12.24 D", "+20.94 D"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02915', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位-2.00 D的近視和老花的病人，全景深為2.00 D，在沒有矯正的情況下，他的近點為25 cm。他能看 得清楚的最遠距離為多少？', '["25 cm", "33.3 cm", "50 cm", "100 cm"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02916', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位-2.00 DS顧客，調節幅度為2.50 D。當他配戴眼鏡後，可看清楚距離為眼前100 cm到20 cm，其景 深為多少？', '["0.50 D", "1.00 D", "1.50 D", "2.00 D"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02917', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一個20歲兩眼不等視的患者，右眼為遠視4.00 D，左眼為遠視8.00 D，當閱讀時視線由鏡片下方通過， 根據普倫提西氏法則（Prentice''s rule），會產生雙眼不一致的稜鏡效應，一般而言下列那一種做法最合適？', '["在右眼配上基底朝上的稜鏡", "在左眼配上基底朝上的稜鏡", "建議病人稍微以頭後仰下巴抬高的姿勢閱讀", "建議病人稍微以頭前傾下巴內縮的姿勢閱讀"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02918', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '遠視+2.00 DS患者，其近點（near point）距離為33 cm。若病人使用最大調節幅度的一半，習慣閱讀距離 為40 cm，請問下列近用眼鏡度數何者最適當？', '["+0.50 DS", "+1.00 DS", "+1.50 DS", "+2.00 DS"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02919', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '顧客配戴-9.00 DS眼鏡（頂點距離15 mm）恰可全矯正。欲看清楚眼前25 cm的影像，配戴隱形眼鏡所需 的調節需求（accommodative demand）和戴眼鏡相差約為多少？', '["戴隱形眼鏡少需0.42 D", "戴隱形眼鏡多需0.75 D", "戴隱形眼鏡多需1.00 D", "戴眼鏡和隱形眼鏡均需相等的調節需求"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02920', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '陳先生的-6.00 D近視眼可以完全被雙焦附加眼鏡（bifocal spectacles）所矯正，透過他的雙焦附加（bifocal add），他的明視範圍（clear range of vision）從100 cm到20 cm，全景深為1.50 D，則他真正的調節幅度 （true amplitude of accomodation）為何？', '["1.00 D", "1.50 D", "2.50 D", "3.50 D"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
