  ('optometrist-moex-02923', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '非球面鏡片（aspheric lens）相較於球面鏡片之優點，何者錯誤？', '["減少正透鏡的中央厚度", "減少負透鏡的邊緣厚度", "減少鏡片重量", "增強正透鏡的影像放大效果"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "17ce3afcfc67", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fd16202528ed", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
